parameters:
Clea: A timid and fearful little girl... that's my true
nature...

Clea: Then why do I fight...? Father's last words were to be
happy... not to fight...

Clea (I have a place to return to... a place to go back
to... there are people waiting for me...)
Clea: It's dazzling... the light... come to think of it...
Clea: The light... at that time... when I met Celis-san...

Clea (That person came out from the light and saved me from
the Psema.)

Clea (Celis-san told me, I became an adventurer so that I
wouldn't give up on myself...)

Clea: I remembered! Why I became an adventurer, why I
fight...!

Clea: I have to go and tell them...! To everyone, to the
people who believed in me!
